{"tid":2175720,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"劉淑儀暗諷新中國？ - 古德明","createTime":"2020-08-26T15:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T18:23:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d645689b0dc4d2e60909e8cf536cfd4ed8adce0f","tid":2175720,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:38:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200825/2NU2TBO3QRAJTKSFMBCTSES4HY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200825%2F2NU2TBO3QRAJTKSFMBCTSES4HY%2F&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhato6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=67a1fa22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200825%2F2NU2TBO3QRAJTKSFMBCTSES4HY%2F&h=628d6944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200825/2NU2TBO3QRAJTKSFMBCTSES4HY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n劉淑儀暗諷新中國？ - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fEHbK77FDwBMCbnbJamR9PUOUp4=/4836x3228/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SSSWBR7LA5CWTEKADXAI3YVYSM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfEHbK77FDwBMCbnbJamR9PUOUp4%3D%2F4836x3228%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSSSWBR7LA5CWTEKADXAI3YVYSM.jpg&h=85d59ad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n八月十一日，新香港行政會議成員劉淑儀在香港電臺《自由風》節目上盛讚新中國說：「我們的防疫工作，比很多民主國家都要好。」她說話太不檢點了。<br />\n<br />\n習近平在中共第十九次全國代表大會報告中說：「我國社會主義民主是維護人民根本利益的最廣泛、最真實、最管用的民主。」中國共產黨新聞網因此還特撰「中國才是當今最大的民主國家」一文。然則劉淑儀怎麼以「我們」新中國或新香港與「民主國家」相對而論？問臺灣總統蔡英文，她一定會說：「我們的防疫工作，其他民主國家很多都比不上。」劉淑儀明白其中分別嗎？<br />\n<br />\n當然，劉淑儀絕對不會說新中國或新香港政府獨裁。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n真情往往流露於疏忽之間。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"53e91d1b1b7fd7df2b2503c1ac4d2308d17ffc2d","tid":2175720,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:42:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/YwIk7z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FYwIk7z.jpg&h=b3b740ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5t5YP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5t5YP.jpg&h=bf84654d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/36/83359569_29c282822a_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F36%2F83359569_29c282822a_c.jpg&h=94bf8981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/b4/ab/48/b4ab480f71b11be5bd9485ca641e0f79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fb4%2Fab%2F48%2Fb4ab480f71b11be5bd9485ca641e0f79.jpg&h=8f82ee00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8WA7EO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn8WA7EO.jpg&h=fe302ad7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7570eeea917bbe4909c4194f23cf519da43b2169","tid":2175720,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"新界北總區副指揮官曾正科交代及回應記者元朗721事件<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2175647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2175647</a>"},{"pid":"0068edc9c8ae32ab6d6c0e5e386e6b41560606ea","tid":2175720,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:23:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2175292/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2175292/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n平常心面對敵人既把戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}